      <h1>Mingjun Wang</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Ph.D. Student · Department of Computer Science and Engineering · The Chinese University of Hong Kong</p>
      <p class="tagline">AI4EDA · 3D IC Design Automation · Circuit Representation Learning · Fault Simulation</p>
      <div class="hero-pills" aria-label="Primary research areas">
