      <p class="hero-bio">
        I am a Ph.D. student in Computer Science and Engineering at The Chinese University of Hong Kong, advised by Prof. Bei Yu. My research primarily focuses on AI4EDA and 3D IC design automation, especially multi-modal circuit understanding, circuit representation learning, flow-oriented timing/power prediction, and scalable fault simulation.
      </p>
